2.00	Andries_Potgieter	Hendrik Potgieter	Andries Hendrik Potgieter, known as Hendrik Potgieter (19 December 1792 - 16 December 1852) was a Voortrekker leader. He served as the first head of state of Potchefstroom from 1840 and 1845 and also as the first head of state of Zoutpansberg from 1845 to 1852.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0e/Voortrekker_Monument_May_2006%2C_IMG_3008.jpg/210px-Voortrekker_Monument_May_2006%2C_IMG_3008.jpg
